OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784593081
OL,3,CBurnham pledges to 'make a difference
OL,4,Cthis year' on cost-of-living
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has promised to "make a
OL,7,Fdifference" to the cost of living
OL,8,Fbefore the end of the year, with the
OL,9,Fexact plans to be announced on his
OL,10,Fsecond day in office.
OL,12,FSpeaking to journalists after he was
OL,13,Fofficially appointed as prime minister
OL,14,Fon Monday, Burnham said that he was
OL,15,F"finalising the details" of his exact
OL,16,Fpolicy plans, but that his government
OL,17,Fwill want to move at a fast pace.
OL,19,F"We just want to do some things that
OL,20,Fpeople will feel and feel quite
OL,21,Fquickly," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784593081
OL,3,CBurnham pledges to 'make a difference
OL,4,Cthis year' on cost-of-living
OL,6,F"It won't solve everything, it won't
OL,7,Ftake all of the pressure off, but it
OL,8,Fjust shows the direction of travel and
OL,9,Fthat we're serious about helping them
OL,10,Fout."
OL,12,FThe new PM suggested that his plans
OL,13,Fcould also include changes to bus
OL,14,Ffares, energy bills and even rent
OL,15,Ffreezes but would not confirm the
OL,16,Fexact policies yet.
OL,18,FBurnham did not comment specifically
OL,19,Fon income tax changes, though he
OL,20,Frecently talked about the potential to
OL,21,Fraise the personal allowance threshold.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
