OL,3,CBurnham pledges to 'make a difference
OL,4,Cthis year' on cost-of-living
OL,6,FThe current threshold sits at #12,570,
OL,7,Fmeaning no income tax is paid on any
OL,8,Fearnings or pension below this amount.
OL,9,FThe threshold was frozen again for the
OL,10,Fcurrent financial year creating a
OL,11,Fstealth tax.
